---
layout: base.njk
pageKey: widget
title: "AI assistant for your website"
permalink: widget.html
description: An always-on AI assistant for your website — answers questions, captures leads, and books, 24/7. One line of code, styled to your brand. Plans from $49/mo after a one-time setup. Try the live demo.
---

{# ===== Hero =========================================================== #}
<section class="section section--tight has-aurora">
  <div class="aurora" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="container container--narrow center">
    <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--center">AI assistant</span>
    <h1 class="section__title">An always-on assistant on your site — from $49/mo</h1>
    <p class="section__lead">
      It answers questions, captures the visitor’s name and contact, and books — all in one
      chat, 24/7. One line of code, styled to your brand, and every lead reaches a real person
      on your team. {{ site.widgetSetup }}, then a simple monthly plan.
    </p>
    <div class="btn-row btn-row--center mt-6">
      <a class="btn btn--primary btn--lg" href="{{ site.links.demo }}">Try the live demo</a>
      <a class="btn btn--ghost btn--lg" href="#plans">See plans</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ===== What it does =================================================== #}
<section class="section section--tight">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section__head section__head--center" data-reveal>
      <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--center">What it does</span>
      <h2 class="section__title">A teammate that never clocks out</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid--auto">
      <article class="card" data-reveal>
        <h3 class="card__title">Answers instantly</h3>
        <p class="card__text">Hours, pricing, services, “do you take my insurance?” — answered from rules you approve, in seconds.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1">
        <h3 class="card__title">Captures every lead</h3>
        <p class="card__text">Name → contact → detail, then it lands in your inbox. Nothing slips away after hours.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="2">
        <h3 class="card__title">Books the next step</h3>
        <p class="card__text">Hands off to your booking flow so an interested visitor becomes a held appointment.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="3">
        <h3 class="card__title">Drops in anywhere</h3>
        <p class="card__text">One &lt;script&gt; tag, isolated styling (Shadow DOM), works on any site. You stay in control.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ===== Plans ========================================================== #}
<section class="section section--tight" id="plans">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section__head section__head--center" data-reveal>
      <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--center">Plans</span>
      <h2 class="section__title">Simple monthly pricing</h2>
      <p class="section__lead">{{ site.widgetSetup }} to build and style it, then pick a plan. Cancel anytime.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid--3">
      {% for plan in site.widgetPlans %}
        <article
          id="{{ plan.key }}"
          class="price{% if plan.featured %} price--popular{% endif %}"
          data-reveal
          data-reveal-delay="{{ loop.index0 }}"
        >
          {% if plan.featured %}<span class="price__flag">Most popular</span>{% endif %}
          <h2 class="price__name">{{ plan.name }}</h2>
          <p class="price__amount">{{ plan.price }} <small>{{ plan.cadence }}</small></p>
          <p class="price__desc">{{ plan.blurb }}</p>
          <ul class="price__features">
            {% for feature in plan.features %}
              <li>{{ feature }}</li>
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
          <div class="price__cta">
            <a
              class="btn {% if plan.featured %}btn--primary{% else %}btn--secondary{% endif %} btn--block"
              href="{{ plan.checkoutUrl if plan.checkoutUrl else site.cta.url }}"
              {% if plan.checkoutUrl %}rel="noopener"{% endif %}
            >
              {% if plan.checkoutUrl %}Start {{ plan.name }} — {{ plan.price }}{{ plan.cadence }}{% else %}Get started{% endif %}
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    <div class="note-card mt-7" data-reveal>
      <span class="note-card__tag">What’s included</span>
      <p>
        Every plan includes hosting, the AI, lead delivery, and keeping it working. The one-time
        setup covers building it, styling it to your brand, and wiring leads to your inbox. Not
        sure which plan? <a href="{{ site.cta.url }}">Start with a free scan</a> and we’ll
        recommend one.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ===== FAQ ============================================================ #}
<section class="section section--tight">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <div class="section__head section__head--center" data-reveal>
      <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--center">FAQ</span>
      <h2 class="section__title">Common questions</h2>
    </div>
    <article class="card mt-6" data-reveal>
      <h3 class="card__title">Does it work on my existing website?</h3>
      <p class="card__text">Yes — it’s one script tag and works on any site, with its own isolated styling so it never clashes with your design.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card mt-6" data-reveal>
      <h3 class="card__title">Will it make things up?</h3>
      <p class="card__text">It answers from what you give us and is set to hand anything it’s unsure about to a real person rather than guess. You approve the boundaries before it goes live.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card mt-6" data-reveal>
      <h3 class="card__title">Where do the leads go?</h3>
      <p class="card__text">Straight to your inbox the moment they’re captured, and on the Pro plan into your CRM. Every lead reaches a real person on your team.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card mt-6" data-reveal>
      <h3 class="card__title">Can I cancel?</h3>
      <p class="card__text">Anytime. The monthly plan covers hosting, the AI, and upkeep; if you cancel we’ll help you wind it down cleanly.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

{# ===== Closing CTA =================================================== #}
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-band" data-reveal>
      <h2 class="cta-band__title">See it on your own site</h2>
      <p class="cta-band__text">
        Try the live demo, then start with a free scan — we’ll set the assistant up, styled to
        your brand, and wire every lead to your inbox.
      </p>
      <div class="btn-row btn-row--center">
        <a class="btn btn--light btn--lg" href="{{ site.links.demo }}">Try the live demo</a>
        <a class="btn btn--secondary btn--lg" href="{{ site.cta.url }}">Get my free scan</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# Structured data: prices are visibly published above, so an Offer is legit. #}
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Service",
  "name": "AI assistant for websites",
  "serviceType": "AI chat assistant",
  "provider": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "Symbio AI", "url": "{{ site.url }}" },
  "areaServed": { "@type": "State", "name": "California" },
  "offers": {
    "@type": "AggregateOffer",
    "priceCurrency": "USD",
    "lowPrice": "49",
    "highPrice": "149",
    "offerCount": "3",
    "url": "{{ site.url }}/widget.html"
  }
}
</script>
